    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n3 \\cot x - \\sqrt{3} = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\cot x = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3} \\Leftrightarrow \\cot x = \\cot \\frac{\\pi}{3} \\Leftrightarrow x = \\frac{\\pi}{3} + k\\pi, (k \\in \\mathbb{Z}).\n$$"
